{"parentUuid":"6c1a58a7-a563-4f6e-8d9b-c36adf895854","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"68ec9cef-6857-4a28-8620-87530be8d16c","agentId":"aside_question-15bdaad69b7e17a9","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"This session is being continued from a previous conversation that ran out of context. The summary below covers the earlier portion of the conversation.\n\nSummary:\n1. Primary Request and Intent:\n   - Find correct motion FB type names for XEC PLC to replace MC_Home/MC_MoveAbsolute/MC_Stop (which don't exist on XEC)\n   - Create PROG_TEST.st standalone servo test program using correct FB types\n   - Generate XG5000-compatible variable CSV (EUC-KR encoding, CRLF, 12 columns)\n   - Test servo operation: reset SW → servo ON, action SW → home → 30° rotation\n   - **Final user intent (most recent)**: \"이미 c#은 다 만들어놨어 plc 쪽만 해\" — C# WPF app is already done, user only wants PLC-side work. User wants PC to control everything, PLC should be minimal/thin I/O only.\n   - User is frustrated with PLC programming complexity and wants to minimize PLC code while controlling from PC\n\n2. Key Technical Concepts:\n   - **APM_xxx FB series** for XEC position control: APM_ORG (home), APM_DST (absolute move), APM_STP (stop), APM_EMG (emergency), APM_FLT (fault reset), APM_PRS (position read/set)\n   - APM parameters: REQ, BASE(=0), SLOT(=9), AXIS(=0), DONE=>, STAT=>\n   - APM_DST additional params: ADDR, SPEED, DWELL, MCODE, POS_SPD, ABS_INC, TIME_SEL\n   - XGT FEnet protocol for direct I/O access: %QW (output word), %IW (input word), %UW (special module word)\n   - Hardware slot layout: 00-04=input(XBE-DC32A), 05-08=output(XBE-TN32A), 09=position control(XBF-PD02A), 10=ethernet(XBL-EMTA)\n   - Servo MC relay = %QX0.0.5 (CPU built-in output, not expansion slot)\n   - 12 stations × 30° index rotation (same as existing Shinjin equipment)\n   - Index position: touch input × 1000 = target position (30° = 30000)\n   - R_TRIG FB had issues on XEC → manual edge detection pattern used instead\n\n3. Files and Code Sections:\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\1cellAssembleMachine\\PLC_ST\\PROG_TEST.st`** — Main test program, rewritten multiple times\n     - Latest version uses manual edge detection, servo MC output, APM FBs\n     ```st\n     (* 리셋SW 수동 엣지 검출 → 서보ON 토글 *)\n     IF %IX0.0.11 AND NOT bResetPrev THEN\n         bServoOn := NOT bServoOn;\n     END_IF;\n     bResetPrev := %IX0.0.11;\n     \n     (* 동작SW 수동 엣지 검출 *)\n     bBtnEdge := %IX0.0.13 AND NOT bBtnPrev;\n     bBtnPrev := %IX0.0.13;\n     \n     (* 서보ON 출력 *)\n     %QX0.0.5 := bServoOn;\n     \n     (* 서보OFF면 스텝 초기화 *)\n     IF NOT bServoOn THEN\n         eStep := 0;\n         RETURN;\n     END_IF;\n     \n     CASE eStep OF\n     0: IF bBtnEdge THEN bOrgReq := TRUE; eStep := 1; END_IF;\n     1: fbOrg(REQ := bOrgReq, BASE := 0, SLOT := 9, AXIS := 0,\n              DONE => bOrgDone, STAT => wOrgStat);\n        IF bOrgDone THEN bOrgReq := FALSE; eStep := 2;\n        ELSIF wOrgStat <> 0 THEN bOrgReq := FALSE; eStep := 0; END_IF;\n     2: IF bBtnEdge THEN bDstReq := TRUE; eStep := 3; END_IF;\n     3: fbDst(REQ := bDstReq, BASE := 0, SLOT := 9, AXIS := 0,\n              ADDR := 30000, SPEED := 50000, DWELL := 0,\n              MCODE := 0, POS_SPD := TRUE, ABS_INC := FALSE,\n              TIME_SEL := 0, DONE => bDstDone, STAT => wDstStat);\n        IF bDstDone THEN bDstReq := FALSE; eStep := 4;\n        ELSIF wDstStat <> 0 THEN bDstReq := FALSE; eStep := 0; END_IF;\n     4: IF bBtnEdge THEN bOrgReq := TRUE; eStep := 1; END_IF;\n     END_CASE;\n     ```\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\1cellAssembleMachine\\PLC_ST\\gen_test_csv.ps1`** — PowerShell CSV generator\n     - Generates EUC-KR + CRLF CSV by reusing example.csv header bytes\n     - Latest version: 17 variables including bResetPrev, bBtnEdge, bBtnPrev, APM_ORG/DST/STP types, UINT for STAT outputs\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\1cellAssembleMachine\\PLC_ST\\example.csv`** — XG5000 variable import CSV\n     - 17 variables for PROG_TEST (latest version)\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\1cellAssembleMachine\\PLC_ST\\GVL.st`** — Updated servo FB section\n     - Changed MC_xxx to APM_xxx types: g_FB_Org(APM_ORG), g_FB_Dst(APM_DST), g_FB_Stp(APM_STP), g_FB_Emg(APM_EMG), g_FB_Flt(APM_FLT), g_FB_Prs(APM_PRS)\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\1cellAssembleMachine\\ARCHITECTURE.md`** — Updated output pin map\n     - Added \"서보MC(%QX0.0.5)\" to slot 00 output description\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\SHINJIN\\1 CELL 조립 장비\\PLC RAW\\ST_XEC\\ST_06_SERVO.st`** — Reference file (existing Shinjin equipment)\n     - 12 stations × 30° index, _D05302 = index target position (touch × 1000), _D05402 = index speed (touch × 100)\n     - _00_IN00 = servo ON / EMO contact input, _00_IN01 = servo ON input\n     - _00_OUT02 = servo ready output (timer-delayed)\n\n   - **`C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\SHINJIN\\1 CELL 조립 장비\\PLC RAW\\ST_XEC\\ST_04_OUTPUT.st`** — Reference output mapping\n     - _00_OUT05 = buzzer, _00_OUT02 = servo ready, _00_OUT10 = EMO SOL\n\n   - **Deleted files** (agent-generated, unnecessary): XEC_MOTION_FB_REFERENCE.md, README_XEC_MOTION.md, XEC_MOTION_INDEX.md, EXTRACTION_SUMMARY.txt, XEC_MOTION_CHEATSHEET.txt, XEC_ST_CODE_EXAMPLES.st\n\n   - **Created but user said to stop**: Features/ServoTest/ServoTestWindow.xaml, ServoTestWindow.xaml.cs — PC-based servo test UI (user said C# is already done)\n\n4. Errors and fixes:\n   - **E0153 \"변수가 잘못 설정 되었습니다\"** for _00_IN00, _00_IN11, _00_IN13:\n     - Fix: Changed to direct variables %IX0.0.0, %IX0.0.11, %IX0.0.13\n   - **W0314 \"펑션 출력 파라미터 할당 연산 처리 중에 변수 타입이 일치\"** for STAT outputs:\n     - Fix: Changed wOrgStat/wDstStat/wStpStat from WORD to UINT type\n   - **Servo not responding to reset switch**: Multiple issues found:\n     - User clarified IN11=reset SW, IN13=action SW (I had them wrong initially)\n     - %IX0.0.0 (servo ON) condition blocked execution → removed initially, then re-added with different approach\n     - User said \"서보온 안되는거 같은데\" — servo ON signal not coming\n   - **Servo MC relay not activating with %QX0.0.2**:\n     - %QX0.0.2 activated small relay but not servo AC MC\n     - User said \"슬롯 변번인디\" — slot numbers are different from reference\n     - Screenshot confirmed: slot 0 = input only modules, outputs start at slot 05\n     - User found %QX0.0.5 (CPU built-in output bit 5) activates servo MC\n   - **R_TRIG not working** — bServoOn never toggled despite %IX0.0.11 changing:\n     - Fix: Replaced R_TRIG with manual edge detection `IF signal AND NOT prev THEN`\n   - **Still not working after manual edge detection**: User's final state showed all values = 0, servo ON not toggling\n     - User got frustrated and said to stop PLC programming, do everything from PC\n\n5. Problem Solving:\n   - **Solved**: XEC motion FB types — APM_ORG/APM_DST/APM_STP confirmed working (CSV import + build successful)\n   - **Solved**: Servo MC relay pin — %QX0.0.5 confirmed by user via forced output test\n   - **Solved**: I/O slot mapping — inputs on slots 0-4, outputs on slots 5-8, position control on slot 9\n   - **Unsolved**: PROG_TEST servo ON toggle not working via program (works with XG5000 forced I/O but not from program logic)\n   - **User decision**: Abandon PLC-side logic complexity, control everything from PC via XGT protocol\n\n6. All user messages:\n   - (Build success output with no errors)\n   - \"이게 중앙에 모터 하나 있는 인덱스 타입인데 한 틱씩 움직일건데 아마\"\n   - \"기존 프로그램에서 제어하는 내용 모르나\"\n   - (interrupted) \"온라인 접속해서 쓰기는 완료되었음\"\n   - \"리셋 눌러도 동작 안함\"\n   - \"온라인 모니터링 엌테하는거임\"\n   - \"0.0.11 은 스위치에 동작하는데 bemo = 0 dla\"\n   - \"13 스위치도 확인됨\"\n   - \"서보온 되야하는거 아님 ?\"\n   - \"서보 드라이버에 릴레이가 하나 있는데\"\n   - \"어케 넣어?\"\n   - \"신호로 되어있는거 아녀 ?\"\n   - \"맵에는 없나\"\n   - \"11 이 리셋 스위치임 이거 한번씩 누를때때마다 한 동작씩\"\n   - \"13 이 동작 스위치고\"\n   - \"서보온하고 돌려야하는거 아니냐 ?\"\n   - \"서보 온 안되는거 같은데\"\n   - (screenshot with Force I/O dialog) \"여기서 어케 하는거임\"\n   - \"2번은 살았다 죽는거 확인했는데 서보에 걸린 AC 릴레이 커다란거는 안켜짐 다른 접점 인거같은데\"\n   - \"out 05 는 뭐임 ?\"\n   - \"기존 넘버링 p025 는 지금 몇번인가 ?\"\n   - \"여섯번째에 물려있는데 그걸로 바꿔볼래\"\n   - \"%QX0.0.5 := bServoOn; 이렇게 하면 되나\"\n   - \"릴레이 안 사는디\"\n   - \"슬롯 변번인디\"\n   - (screenshot) \"에 출력 05 살리니 서보 마그네틱 살어 이거 핀맵에 반영해줘\"\n   - \"근데 스위치 누르면 동작안함\"\n   - \"%IX0.0.13 = 0, %IX0.0.11 = 0, rtReset.Q = 0, bServoOn = 0, %QX0.0.5 = 0; bServoOn = 0, bServoOn = 0, eStep = 0 서버온으로 안감\"\n   - \"바뀜\" (confirming %IX0.0.11 changes when pressed)\n   - \"아 그냥 아무것도 짜지말고 PC 에서 다 하게 프로그램 하나 짜라 그냥\"\n   - \"맵은 그대로 하면 되나\"\n   - \"정지\"\n   - \"이미 c# 은 다 만들어놨어 plc 쪽만 해\"\n\n7. Pending Tasks:\n   - **PLC side minimal program**: User wants PLC-side code only (not C#), minimal/thin I/O approach so PC can control everything via XGT protocol\n   - The memory map (MW100~501) should remain as-is\n   - Need to create minimal PLC programs that:\n     - Map physical I/O to MW area (PROG_IO_MAP) so PC can read/write\n     - Relay servo commands from MW300 to APM_xxx FBs (PROG_SERVO using APM types)\n     - Keep safety/watchdog (PROG_SAFETY)\n   - PROG_SERVO.st needs to be updated from MC_xxx to APM_xxx types\n   - The C# WPF app is already built by the user — do NOT create C# code\n\n8. Current Work:\n   I was in the middle of creating a C# WPF ServoTestWindow when the user said \"정지\" (stop) and then \"이미 c#은 다 만들어놨어 plc 쪽만 해\" (C# is already done, just do the PLC side). The ServoTestWindow.xaml and .xaml.cs files were already created but should be ignored/deleted.\n   \n   The user wants to abandon the complex PROG_TEST standalone test approach and instead have minimal PLC programs that allow the PC (C# WPF app, already built) to control everything via XGT FEnet protocol. The memory map (MW100~501 for I/O, servo, watchdog) should remain as designed.\n\n9. Optional Next Step:\n   Based on user's last message \"이미 c#은 다 만들어놨어 plc 쪽만 해\" — Update the PLC ST programs to use APM_xxx types instead of MC_xxx:\n   - Update **PROG_SERVO.st*